---
title: Beef Rogan Josh & Garlic Rice with Kachumber Salad
description: Dive into the rich flavours of this indulgent curry, with succulent beef simmered in a symphony of warm spices. Garlic rice is the perfect carrier to soak up all the sauce, and a kachumber salad on the side offers a refreshing crunch and zap that elevates every bite.
